{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-spanish-fundamentals/spanish-alphabet-general-review","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Pročitao sam ovaj pregled osnova španskog jezika.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-review-spanish-fundamentals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Vreme je da se pregleda španski alfabet i posebni znaci.</p>\n<h2>Španski alfabet</h2>\n<p>Molimo vas da poświęćujete vreme za čitanje ove tabele. Ona prikazuje svako slovo i njegove varijante malog i velikog slova, kao i njegovo ime.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Mala slova</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Velika slova</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Ime</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">a</td>\n<td align=\"left\">A</td>\n<td align=\"left\">a</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">b</td>\n<td align=\"left\">B</td>\n<td align=\"left\">be</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">c</td>\n<td align=\"left\">C</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ce</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">d</td>\n<td align=\"left\">D</td>\n<td align=\"left\">de</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">e</td>\n<td align=\"left\">E</td>\n<td align=\"left\">e</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">f</td>\n<td align=\"left\">F</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ef</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">g</td>\n<td align=\"left\">G</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ge</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">h</td>\n<td align=\"left\">H</td>\n<td align=\"left\">hače</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">i</td>\n<td align=\"left\">I</td>\n<td align=\"left\">i</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">j</td>\n<td align=\"left\">J</td>\n<td align=\"left\">jota</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">k</td>\n<td align=\"left\">K</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ka</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">l</td>\n<td align=\"left\">L</td>\n<td align=\"left\">el e</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">m</td>\n<td align=\"left\">M</td>\n<td align=\"left\">em e</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">n</td>\n<td align=\"left\">N</td>\n<td align=\"left\">en e</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">ñ</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Ñ</td>\n<td align=\"left\">eñe</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">o</td>\n<td align=\"left\">O</td>\n<td align=\"left\">o</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">p</td>\n<td align=\"left\">P</td>\n<td align=\"left\">pe</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">q</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Q</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ku</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">r</td>\n<td align=\"left\">R</td>\n<td align=\"left\">er e</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">s</td>\n<td align=\"left\">S</td>\n<td align=\"left\">e se</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">t</td>\n<td align=\"left\">T</td>\n<td align=\"left\">te</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">u</td>\n<td align=\"left\">U</td>\n<td align=\"left\">u</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">v</td>\n<td align=\"left\">V</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ve pequeña</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">w</td>\n<td align=\"left\">W</td>\n<td align=\"left\">doble ve</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">x</td>\n<td align=\"left\">X</td>\n<td align=\"left\">ekvis</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">y</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Y</td>\n<td align=\"left\">je</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">z</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Z</td>\n<td align=\"left\">zeta</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Imajte na umu da su neka od ovih imena uobičajena u Južnoj Americi, ali mogu varirati/razlikovati se na različitim područjima.</p>\n<h2>Specijalni znaci</h2>\n<p>U Kihispaniji, pitanja i uzviknici se pišu otvarajućim i zatvarajućim znakovima.</p>\n<p>Kada neke jezike zahtevaju samo zatvarajući znak pitanja (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">?</span>) ili uzvičnik (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">!</span>), Kihispania takođe zahteva podignut znak pitanja (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿</span>) na početku pitanja i podignuti uzvičnik (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">¡</span>) na početku uzvika. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Za pitanje, ćeš napisati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo estás?</span> (\"How are you?\").</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Kao iznenađenje, napisat ćeš <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¡Gracias!</span> (\"Thank you!\").</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Početni markeri pomažu u predviđanju zvuka i strukture rečenice od samog početka.</p>\n<p>Prvih deset brojeva</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Španski</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Engleski</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">0</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cero</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Zero</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Uno</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">One</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Dos</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Two</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tres</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Three</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cuatro</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Four</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cinco</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Five</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Seis</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Six</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">7</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Siete</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Seven</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">8</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ocho</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\">Eight</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">9</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Nueve</sp